node.text:
Hi guys!!! 
• Today we thought together about how it could shape our visual identity!! 😬
• After years I thought it was time to reFRESH our logo!  the color takes up the FRESHness both in style and color…🥶
• From which part of our username derives!  then a distinctive Apple element could not be missing!  the classic leaf, stainless brand…
• I think the logo is beautiful, clearly visible, impactful and definitely hooked! 
•What do you think? 
• I'd love to hear your opinion! ✍🏻 
👉🏻 find 3 photos, the first two are the logo in the new design, the third is the previous logo!
.
.
.
Ph. @applesfresh #logo #newlogo #newsapple #Applenews #logotype #logodesigner #logodesigns #logodesigner #logos #Apple #applelogo #applesfresh #fresh #news #appledesignworld

Which app can you not give up? 🤔
